{
  "stem": "11089.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm still doing it. 1953, I started to teach here in Toronto-- two different schools.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I started with Eitz Chaim for 10 years.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the rest, 30 years in the associated Hebrew schools.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the last few years, I am supervisor, or principal.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I'm still involved with the children.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am a very happy person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I am a very happy person.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's a very, very-- I-- I was asked this question different way, but your question is a hard question.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But to me, I saw plenty of sorrows, plenty of sadnesses-- sadness.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I, to me, to be happy is more important than to be sad.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What am I going to gain aggravating myself from the past?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Am I going to gain something from it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "From the past, I learn the present.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And from the present, I'm learning what to do with the future.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I believe the only way to guarantee the survival of our people is through education.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I saw the loss of our people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I want to see, and I'm seeing, the up-- the coming up, the growing up of our people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "From sorrow, to joy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[SPEAKING YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "From sadness to happy days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And this is also why I took my job as a children-- to stay with children.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Children are happy.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Children are telling the truth, when they are little at least.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Children are singing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Children are dancing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Children are cute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Even sometimes, you have some aggravation, but the simple, the joy, is more than aggravation.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "So by being with them, happy, I forget-- I forget the sorrows.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What am I going to gain by being sad?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What am I going to gain to have some claims, or anger against God?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know-- I know we suffered.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
